<h2>Children's Volunteer of the Month - June</h2><div id="sermon-info" class="sermon"><ul class="sermon-buttons"></ul><!-- .sermon-buttons --><p class="sermon-meta">Posted Jun 14th, 2013 &nbsp;  </p></div><!-- .sermon --><div id="text"><p>Adventure Kids, the dynamic children's program of Portland Christian Center (Portland, Oregon) has been blessed with incredible volunteers who serve in a variety of children's activities and programs within the children's department.</p><p>Last Sunday, we honored Dave and Krissy Fillis as our Adventure Kids Volunteers of the Month. Both Dave and Krissy have actively and faithfully served our children's ministries since coming into the church five years ago. They currently team lead our Royal Ranger Clubs for boys and Mpact clubs for girls on Wednesday evenings.&nbsp;</p><p><img src="http://f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/uploaded/p/0e2220705_1371230100_profile--volunteer--dave-and-krissy-fillis.jpg" alt="Profile : Volunteer : Dave and Krissy Fillis" title="Profile : Volunteer : Dave and Krissy Fillis"><strong>Thank you, Dave and Krissy,</strong> for your dedicated leadership. Your initiative, commitment and passion for your students and leaders is invaluable!</p><p><a href="/ministries/children/" class="button">About Adventure Kids</a></p><p><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/ministries/children/serving-opportunities-with-children/" class="button">Ways You Can Serve!</a></p></div>